# Raw scrape cache (scripts/scrape-brands.py) — a re-run convenience so the
# scraper doesn't re-hit the live sites, not needed to run the seed itself
# (which only reads the small normalised scripts/scraped/*-catalog.json
# files, tracked below). The Outfitters raw feed alone is ~15MB, too large
# to be worth committing.
scripts/scraped/*/

